{"color":"DEFAULT","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":true,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"\n\n\nEmail not displaying correctly? View it online\n\n\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nBuild agentic applications with new Gemini 2.5 Flash capabilities\n\n\n\n\n\nTry Gemini 2.5 Flash\n\n\n\n\n\nJust announced at Google I/O! New models and capabilities for developers to build agentic applications:\n \nPrototype faster with Gemini 2.5 Pro: Instantly generate web apps with AI at their core from just a prompt using the Gemini API\nNative audio with the Live API: Create voice agents with more natural spoken interactions in 24 languages\nModel Context Protocol (MCP) support: Integrate open source tools with native SDK support for MCP definitions\n \nThe most exciting part? Now you can combine Gemini model reasoning with tools to create more capable agents. Try it out in Google AI Studio and explore more of our updates from Google I/O.\n\n\n\n\n\nGenerate apps with Gemini 2.5 Pro code assistance\n\n\n\n\nPrototype faster in AI Studio with Gemini 2.5 Pro code generation, tightly optimized with the Google Gen AI SDK. Instantly generate web apps for the Gemini API from text, image, or video prompts. Deploy to Cloud Run to start testing and scaling your app.\nGenerate apps in AI Studio\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nBuild conversational agents with the Live API and tools\n\n\n\n\nUse native audio and multimodal reasoning to build more capable agents. Improvements to search and function calling, and new features like URL context and native MCP support, make it easier to build agentic apps with tools.\nPrototype with the Live API\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n Catch up on Google I/O highlights \n\n\n\n\nJoin the Google AI Studio team and unpack the latest Gemini models, AI Studio upgrades, and new developer tools unveiled at Google I/O in a special episode of Release Notes.\nWatch the video\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nFireside chat with Demis Hassabis \nExplore the future of AI and its impact on our world with Demis Hassabis, co-founder and CEO of Google DeepMind.\nWatch the fireside chat\n\n\n\n\n\n\nIt\u2019s an exciting time to be building with the Gemini API. To explore all the new updates from Google I/O check out this recap blog. \nThanks, \nThe Google AI Studio team\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n© 2025 Google Ireland Ltd, Gordon House, Barrow Street, Dublin 4, Ireland.\nThis email was sent to likedbig@gmail.com because you signed up to receive emails about Google AI. If you do not wish to receive these emails, please unsubscribe.\n\n\n","title":"","userEditedTimestampUsec":1748016814502000,"createdTimestampUsec":1748016814502000,"textContentHtml":"<br /><br /><br /><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Email not displaying correctly? <\/span><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">View it online<\/span><\/p><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000